"user":{"login":"BorisBoutillier","id":18518188,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4NTE4MTg4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/18518188?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier","html_url":"https://github.com/BorisBoutillier","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2024-10-15T09:54:47Z","updated_at":"2024-10-15T09:57:01Z","body":"I have been able to bisect the problem and the first bad commit is 675f8ad40380966e3cc9176e95965538df621810, associated to PR #14848\n\nThe updated example I used is \n```rust\nuse bevy::prelude::*;\n\nfn main() {\n    App::new()\n        .add_plugins(DefaultPlugins)\n        .add_systems(Startup, setup)\n        .add_systems(Update, text_rotation_system)\n        .run();\n}\n\nfn setup(mut commands: Commands, asset_server: Res<AssetServer>) {\n    commands.spawn(Camera2dBundle::default());\n    commands.spawn((TextBundle::from_section(\n        \"abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz\",\n        TextStyle {\n            font: asset_server.load(\"fonts/FiraSans-Bold.ttf\"),\n            font_size: 40.0,\n            ..default()\n        },\n    )\n    .with_style(Style {\n        align_self: AlignSelf::Center,\n        justify_self: JustifySelf::Center,\n        ..default()\n    }),));\n}\n\nfn text_rotation_system(time: Res<Time>, mut query: Query<&mut Transform, With<Text>>) {\n    for mut transform in &mut query {\n        let seconds = time.elapsed_seconds();\n        transform.rotation = Quat::from_rotation_z(seconds / 2.0);\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThat is the best I can do with my current knowledge, hope this helps.\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bevyengine/bevy/issues/comments/2413431823/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"BorisBoutillier","id":18518188,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4NTE4MTg4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/18518188?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier","html_url":"https://github.com/BorisBoutillier","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BorisBoutillier/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"actor":{"login":"mockersf","id":8672791,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjg2NzI3OTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8672791?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mockersf","html_url":"https://github.com/mockersf","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mockersf/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/use